entries.femaleVariant: This oughta work.
Great – so why're we here?
Well? So why're we here, exactly?
Heard Kerry got himself a buck-a-mansion here. Done well.
Never did like him outright, no reservations, did you?
So, want me to head to his deluxe dump?
Always did have some beef with him, didn't you?
entries.maleVariant: You always did have some beef with him, didn't you?

entries.femaleVariant: Me? Nah, he's the one who couldn't decide whether to fuck me or boot me outta the band.
So I gotta hit Kerry's digs, look around, critique the drapes?
Know what they're writin' about him? He's depressed, attempted suicide.
What, really worried he wants to hurt himself?
Who knows. Either way, could give him some pointers.
What did you want?
Clashing visions?
OK, don't think I need to know any more.
Which were you hopin' for?
Clash of the titan visionaries?
OK. Don't wanna know any more.
Problem with Ker was he had a dick – meanin' I wasn't interested – but he was missin' the balls.
Only posed as a rebel to fit in, actually desperate not to step on any toes.
Arasaka's especially.
So, want me to head to his deluxe dump?
You get along better with the rest of the band?
You get along any better with the rest of the band?
Others didn't give a rat's dick about me.
Nancy just enjoyed controlling us – treated us all like sex-scavenging halfwits.
Which was kinda true for Henry, actually.
Tried to get with Denny – thing was, those two rarely shared the same state of consciousness at once.
Meanin' you wanna go "in person?" Gotta hand you the reins again?
Yes. Behaved myself last time, didn't I? I think I warrant another furlough for good behavior.
No way. Made an exception for Rogue.
Uh-huh. First for Kerry, then for who?
OK. Wanna know what to expect, though.
No way, nuh-uh. Rogue was special, made an exception.
OK. But I wanna know what you plan to do.
Mhm. First Rogue, now Kerry. Who's next on the list of conjugal visits?
entries.maleVariant: Heh, uh-huh. First Rogue, now Kerry. Who's next on the list of conjugal visits?

entries.femaleVariant: True, Rogue was wholly different. Thought you understood that.
OK. If you change your mind, lemme know.
Nothin' stupid, I promise. Just wanna see how he's doin'.
Nobody. Just so happens the list of people I consider friends, and who're still alive, is pretty damn short.
Exactly why I need to talk to Kerry.
How you plan to tell him it's you?
V, Ker was always dealing with personal shit. That's why, in spite of everything else, we got along.
Don't worry. I'll play it by ear, sensitively. First things first – we gotta get into that house.
OK. Just lemme know when you wanna take the wheel.
Could be dealin' with some real personal shit right now, might not be the best time to mess with his head.
Attempted suicide? Care to explain?
What was that about attempted suicide?
Amateur hour. Didn't even cobble together the right audience.
Tried to put a bullet through his skull in his room. Bodyguard took his gun like candy from a baby.
Could just be the rumor mill.
Sure, could. But I wanna know.
Where'd you hear anything about Kerry?
In and about town. Screamsheets're full of shit about 'im... Oh, right, you weren't around.
Mhm, your boys' night out. So what, wanna pay him a visit?
entries.maleVariant: Mhm, your big night out. So what, wanna pay him a visit?

entries.femaleVariant: Yep. Seems as good a time as any.
Thousand times nope, don't trust you.
entries.maleVariant: Thousand times no, don't trust you.

entries.femaleVariant: Honestly, kinda surprised you'd even ask.
Nope. Don't trust you.
Had to try – but I guess I'm not surprised. Dick.
